OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Steve Wright's Sunday Love Songs opened
OL,6, with a tribute to the BBC Radio 2      
OL,7, presenter, who died earlier this week. 
OL,9,FPresenting a special episode of the    
OL,10,Fshow, Liza Tarbuck said the show was   
OL,11,Fgoing on but "without the chief".      
OL,13,FShe also read out tributes from        
OL,14,Flisteners to the DJ.                   
OL,16,FWright's final show was last Sunday,   
OL,17,Fwhen he hosted a pre-recorded special  
OL,18,FValentine's Day edition of his Love    
OL,19,FSongs programme. He passed away on     
OL,20,FMonday at the age of 69.               
